---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="洞察 | ARM Management"
  description="监管更新、司法管辖区指南及市场情报——为国际运营商撰写。"
  lang="zh"
  canonicalPath="/insights"
>
<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1456324504439-367cee3b3c32?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">洞察</span>
      <h1>国际业务<br />情报中心。</h1>
      <p>监管更新、司法管辖区指南及市场情报——为需要准确、可操作信息的运营商撰写。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div style="background:#F7F3EC;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-left:3px solid #B8960C;padding:28px 32px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:40px">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">内容以英语提供</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px">我们的分析和司法管辖区指南目前以英语发布。该部分的翻译已在计划中——请查阅以下可用资源。</p>
        <a href="/insights" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block">查看英文洞察 →</a>
      </div>
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">特色资源</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">2026年——36个司法管辖区税务比较</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">我们覆盖的所有市场的企业所得税和增值税的可排序、可搜索比较。</p>
      <div class="btn-row reveal" style="justify-content:flex-start;margin-top:26px">
        <a href="/insights/2026-corporate-tax-vat-comparison" class="btn-primary">打开比较 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">对特定司法管辖区有疑问？</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">我们的顾问可以直接用您的语言讨论您的情况。</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn-primary">与顾问交流 →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Base>
